subject: Basketball
College Athletics
NCAA Basketball Tournament (Men)
lead_paragraph: The 67-58 loss to No. 20 Louisiana State in the quarterfinals of the Southeastern Conference tournament jeopardizes Kentucky’s streak of 17 consecutive N.C.A.A. appearances.
